      SDSU Hosts 2023 Mountain West Softball Championship The 2023 Mountain West Softball Championship is coming to the SDSU Softball Stadium  May 11-13!           Chelsea Investment Corporation to Develop First Affordable Housing Project at SDSU Mission Valley The development will include 182 affordable units and a community-serving childcare center, and is expected to break ground as early as 2025           Empowering Student-Athletes: Aztec Alumni Rally to Find NIL Solution SDSU alumnus Jeff Smith ('94) joined other alumni, business and community leaders to find a San Diego State style solution for NIL. Today, SDSU men's and women's basketball participate in community service events that benefit the local community as part of their NIL deals.           Win a Replica SDSU Baseball Jersey Gear up for Summer! The May Aztec for Life Monthly Prize winner will receive a $100 Aztec Shops gift card.            JMS Alumna Jill Nash Appointed By President Biden to Fulbright Foreign Scholarship Board The Fulbright Program is the flagship international educational exchange program sponsored by the U.S. Government.
